the people with their tasks. Or explore the world on your own to find treasures, resources and coins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movement options:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The entire island can be explored freely, which includes on foot, on horseback, in and under water, in the air, with a jetpack, with a paraglider and of course on the back of a Pegasus.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the mysteries of Pegasus Island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937140/extras/f65e6fd5603accc25019237e273032bf.avif?t=1770839130\" width=600 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937140/extras/153d8bb502d724b8d9c4138b2e71a639.poster.avif?t=1770839130\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937140/extras/153d8bb502d724b8d9c4138b2e71a639.webm?t=1770839130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937140/extras/153d8bb502d724b8d9c4138b2e71a639.mp4?t=1770839130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937140/extras/facc89f48dbc8838a4f7b15e4360f2c6.poster.avif?t=1770839130\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937140/extras/facc89f48dbc8838a4f7b15e4360f2c6.webm?t=1770839130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937140/extras/facc89f48dbc8838a4f7b15e4360f2c6.mp4